title: 3 Presidents Swoop Into Pennsylvania, in a Clash That Transcends 2022
description: As the midterms come to a close, the establishment politics of the two most recent Democratic presidents will meet the disruptive force of the last Republican one, with control of Congress at stake.
media:credit: Hilary Swift for The New York Times
media:description: Former President Donald J. Trump will rally Republicans on Saturday in southwest Pennsylvania, while President Biden and former President Barack Obama will speak to Democrats in Philadelphia.
